title: David Chang Plants New Restaurant in Century City With Super Peach by Momofuku
summary: Super Peach is ripe to celebrate “American dining through the Momofuku lens with a collaborative, playful menu from David Chang and the Momofuku culinary team” to reflect the culture of L.A. and beyond.

title: MrBeast and Mira Sorvino to Be Honored, Zachary Levi to Perform at New York Operation Smile Gala
summary: The event is set to host more than 400 at Sony Hall in Times Square on Wednesday evening. Pritika Swarup, model, influencer and Prakti Beauty founder, has been tapped to serve as the gala host.
